{
  "stem": "9168.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in the Grand Hotel, of course, we had the, the dining room there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we would all meet in the lobby at the Grand Hotel after 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were taken there by a US Army bus always, because of the security.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we probably had [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] a-- we probably had the opportunity to go various places.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, I know that we did have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we had to have orders cut.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If it was a long weekend where the counsel were preparing for the next segment of testimony-- Friday, Saturday, and Sunday, for example-- we could go to Prague, or wherever in our little group we decided we'd like to go that weekend.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It could be-- it could've been in Germany, and was many times-- to resort areas in Germany-- Garmisch, Berchtesgaden, which was where Hitler's Eagle's Nest was.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And our favorite place was Prague, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we would go on a train with our orders, German train, maybe about 20 of us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we would spend the weekend in Prague.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I remember on one occasion, the last-- we loved Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We loved the people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because if we didn't know where we were going, where we wanted to go in the old city, they would walk 10 blocks with us to show us where we wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we would-- they, they never had dinner served in the hotels in Prague, or anywhere in Europe, until 8:00 PM.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That was the dinner hour-- 9:00 PM, 10:00 PM.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They had these wonderful Viennese orchestras, you know, that played during the dinner hour.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we wouldn't get back to our rooms in the hotel until 1:00 or 2:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
